      "content": "I've never been able to pull of desperado as my main damage source on a20 consistently. Even with snecko eye. Its too hard to make a small hermit deck that can loop desperado and still get enough block for the heart. I found this card to be at its best when i'm just taking it in act 1 to do 10 for 1 and maybe 20 for 2 later in the fight.",
